                            <h1 class="text-center">Build up a Shield from Parts</h1> 
                        


                        <!-- ./build.ejs starts -->
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-12">
        <p>Choose the parts from the questions below and watch how your blazon is built up. If you are new to heraldry
        then you may wish to use the "Teach Me" option under the "Learn" menu - this has a small number of options and will carefully guide you through the process.
        This page gives you access to many more feature, but it does need you to answer many more questions!</p>
        <p class="lead">Pay careful attention to the blazon as it is built up in the textarea - this will help you learn
        blazonry!</p>
    </div>
